From d5675fe7b6ba3aafb310c626f38f37270e107aa9 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Fri, 10 Jul 2026 03:47:23 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add "Support Our Florida Community" business map page
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

New trilingual /community page matching the live site's design system
(navy/blue/gold, existing Header/Footer/ChatWidget), built on the
interactive map + search prototype reviewed earlier:

- Real Leaflet + OpenStreetMap map with 12 placeholder FL businesses
- Search matches business name, address, and type of business, with
  the matched name substring highlighted so it's always clearly visible
- Category filters (Realtors, Lenders, Contractors, Shops, Auto, Salon)
- Full EN/ES/RU translations added to lib/dictionaries.ts, incl. a new
  Community nav link in the header
- RESPA-aware compliance disclaimer and the existing "We Care About Our
  Community"™ trademark line in the footer

Business data in lib/communityBusinesses.ts is placeholder/demo content
pending a real intake flow and the RESPA legal review flagged in the
project handoff notes.
